{"id":220986,"date":[{"year":1951,"month":4,"day":2}],"page":"6","source":"","region":"","masthead":"","special_issue":"文学界","column":"","genre":"","count":"740","ytitle":"","mtitle":"我要快点长大","ftitle":"","authors":["梅志"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"梅志"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一向"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"家里乱糟糟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻箱倒笼的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十年没见过阳光的东西都跳出来了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小儿子很高兴"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爬在地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸摸这件奇怪的花棉袄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又摸摸那件很大很大的长袍。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后来可不知怎么一弄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈同哥哥姊姊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可把它们一包一包的全送走了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他实在弄不懂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就拉着妈妈问:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"‘这些你们拿去换糖吃还是换火柴?’"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不，小儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们捐送给没衣穿的难民了。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想到那些不穿衣服。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"包在妈妈怀里的小难民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小儿子马上脱掉自己的绒线衫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要妈妈为他一起捐掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“不，小儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这件你还得穿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈忙得很，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没功夫同你结新的。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但过不久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姊姊又回家来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻着每一个角落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻出了许多宝贝玩意儿:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有缺嘴的剪刀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有破了的铜壶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有生锈的铁条，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有………………"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杂七杂八一大堆。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小儿子看见很好笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么一向老爱骂玩脏东西的姊姊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己也在玩不干净的东西。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"姊姊还把那些东西装了一口袋"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说是要送给政府造子弹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好多打美国狼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个，小儿子顶赞成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赶快将自己的铜铃、锡兵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"双手送上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“也替我做几颗小子弹。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“好，小弟弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你快点长大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要介绍你做个少年儿童队员。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"再过不久，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥身上扣着一朵大红花回来了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说是参加了军事干校。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小儿子望着那朵大红花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心里真羡慕，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就问哥哥:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“怎么参加?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我可不可以也得一朵大红花?”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哥哥说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“你还年纪小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我参加了是要去学开飞机"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开坦克"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开兵舰"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还要学开大炮。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我学好了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就可以保卫祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也可以保护你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"现在你还太小，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你要参加，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要等你和我一样长到十七岁。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小儿子真不高兴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么一定要十七岁?"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开飞机我可多愿意呀!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开坦克也不差，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是兵舰大炮样样都好要，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎么不让我参加!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"妈妈这时可塞给他一个大馒头，说:"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“孩子，按时吃东西，不要吃另食，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你就可以长得高大长得结实。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十七岁很快就要到的。”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“是的，妈妈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我要快点长大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就长得同哥哥一样大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就十七岁了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我就也要参加!”"}]}